com.camerontec.catalys.core.session

Class SessionDialects

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.SessionDialects

  • public class SessionDialects
extends Object
    Bean giving read access to session dialects. These dialects are set on the session by passing a SessionConfiguration object to Session.configure(IConfiguration).
